flavor_text_entries.red:
Stores thermal
energy in its
body. Swims at a steady 8 knots
even in intensely
cold waters.
flavor_text_entries.blue:
Stores thermal
energy in its
body. Swims at a steady 8 knots
even in intensely
cold waters.
flavor_text_entries.yellow:
Its entire body is
a snowy-white.
Unharmed by even intense cold, it
swims powerfully
in icy waters.
flavor_text_entries.gold:
Its streamlined
body has little
drag in water. The colder the
temperature, the
friskier it gets.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
It loves frigid
seas with ice
floes. It uses its long tail to
change swimming
direction quickly.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
It sleeps under
shallow ocean
waters during the day, then looks
for food at night
when it's cold.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
DEWGONG loves to snooze on bitterly
cold ice.
The sight of this POKéMON sleeping on a glacier was mistakenly thought to be
a mermaid by a mariner long ago.

flavor_text_entries.ultra-sun:
It swims through the ocean at a speed of eight
knots, searching for Pokémon that will become
its prey. It’s especially fond of Wishiwashi.

in its body temperature helps its digestion.
